'''Soul Blazer''' features six main acts, each with multiple interconnected areas. This page documents the map structure, area data, and world progression.

== World Structure ==

The game is divided into six acts, each consisting of:
* A Hub town (populated by releasing souls)
* Multiple dungeon areas
* A boss arena
* Connection to the Master's Shrine

