== Special Map Features ==

=== Transformation Zones ===
Certain maps enable animal transformation:
* GreenWood: Mole tunnels ($07-$0A)
* St. Elle's: Angel clouds ($0F)
* Model Town: Mouse holes ($12-$14)
* Seabed: Mermaid waters ($16-$1A)

=== Secret Areas ===
Hidden rooms accessible via:
* Invisible walls (walk through certain tiles)
* Soul release triggers
* Item-based access

=== Progressive Unlocks ===
Areas unlock as souls are released:
* Bridges appear
* Doors unlock
* Paths clear
* NPCs grant access

